sentences: Valera has released four albums with K Records and now works on multimedia projects where she resides in Olympia, Washington.

Most recently, she performed at the Time-Based Art Festival in Portland, Oregon, the Whitney Museum of American Art in New York City, the Centre Georges Pompidou, La Cité Internationale Universitaire de Paris, and La Gaîté Lyrique in Paris.
She is currently working and teaching Electronic Media and Graphic Design at The Evergreen State College in Olympia, WA.
The Soft And The Hardcore (2005, K Records)
Where Are We From (2011, K Records)
My Love (Justin Timberlake cover) on Reprises Inrocks no. 1 (2007, Les Inrockuptibles)
remix of Mirah's song Make It Hot on Joyride: Remixes (2006, K Records)
